OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBig rise in students asking
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor hardship cash          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The number of students seeking extra   
OL,6, money because of financial problems    
OL,7, doubled in 25% of English universities 
OL,8, in the last academic year.             
OL,10,FMore than 75% of universities that     
OL,11,Fresponded to a Universities UK (UUK)   
OL,12,Fsurvey had seen an increase in requests
OL,13,Ffor hardship funding.                  
OL,15,FStudents relying on part-time work were
OL,16,Fmost affected during lockdowns.        
OL,18,FThe government said it had made an     
OL,19,Fextra #85m available for students "in  
OL,20,Fthe greatest need" in 2020-21.         
